Topic: Life after work

Questions:
1. What will you usually do after work at home?

2. Will you try to learn some new knowledge or skills after work in order to improve your work performance and efficiency? If yes, what kind of skills would you like to learn? What is your motivation?

3. How would you balance “veg out” and “improve yourself” at your leisure time?

4. Do you think you are a person who could try not to do anything and veg out entire day at home?


## 重點單字

1. veg out: 放鬆，無所事事
2. improve: 改進，提升
3. balance: 平衡
4. motivation: 動機，動力